*Opet* je svanulo. (The sun rose again.)
*Ponovo* je počela da se vrti muzika. (The music started playing again.)
*Opet* smo se sreli. (We met again.)
*Ponovo* se vratila u grad. (She returned to the city again.)
*Opet* se suočavamo sa problemom. (We are facing the problem again.)
*Ponovo* smo se našli u istoj situaciji. (We found ourselves in the same situation again.)